author: Written by: FOX8Live.com Staff
title: Vitter, Edwards in gubernatorial runoff
text:
(WVUE) - BATON ROUGE, La. (AP) - GOP's David Vitter advances to runoff in Louisiana governor's race against Democrat John Bel Edwards.
The runoff is Nov. 21.
